thread.title: Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3

title: Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3
text:
> Sports Back home, Blue Jays break out to beat Royals 11-8 in Game 3 Kansas City Royals starting pitcher Johnny Cueto reacts after Toronto Blue Jays' Troy Tulowitzki hit a three-run homer during the third inning in Game 3 of baseball's American League Championship Series on Monday, Oct. 19, 2015, in Toronto. (Chris Young/The Canadian Press via AP) MANDATORY CREDIT The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
